title: Grateful Dead Live at Shoreline Amphitheatre on 1990-06-16
taper: Rick Katzeff and Dave Brotman and Marco Fanari and Ted Mattes
description:
Set 1

Let The Good Times Roll-> Truckin'-> Touch Of Gray, Mama Tried-> Big River, Friend Of The Devil, Cassidy, Big Boss Man, One More Saturday Night

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, We Can Run But We Can't Hide-> Estimated Prophet-> Terrapin Station-> Jam-> Drums-> Space-> China Doll-> Sugar Magnolia-, E: It's All Over Now Baby Blue
